sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Investidor
    participant ERC as ERC1155Facet
    participant Freeze as FreezeStorage
    participant Asset as AssetStorage
    participant Balance as ERC1155Storage
    participant Router as ComplianceRouterFacet
    participant Module as IComplianceModule
    participant Supply as SupplyStorage

    User->>ERC: safeTransferFrom(from, to, tokenId, amount)

    Note over ERC: Etapa 1 — Verificações Globais
    ERC->>Freeze: globalPaused?
    Freeze-->>ERC: false
    ERC->>Freeze: globalFreeze[from]?
    Freeze-->>ERC: false
    ERC->>Freeze: globalFreeze[to]?
    Freeze-->>ERC: false

    Note over ERC: Etapa 2 — Verificações do Ativo
    ERC->>Asset: configs[tokenId].exists?
    Asset-->>ERC: true
    ERC->>Asset: configs[tokenId].paused?
    Asset-->>ERC: false
    ERC->>Freeze: assetFreeze[tokenId][from]?
    Freeze-->>ERC: false
    ERC->>Freeze: lockupExpiry[tokenId][from] <= agora?
    Freeze-->>ERC: true

    Note over ERC: Etapa 3 — Verificação de Saldo
    ERC->>Balance: partitions[tokenId][from].free
    Balance-->>ERC: 1000
    ERC->>Freeze: frozenAmount[tokenId][from]
    Freeze-->>ERC: 200
    Note over ERC: disponível = 1000 - 200 = 800 >= amount ✓

    Note over ERC: Etapa 4 — Verificação de Compliance
    ERC->>Asset: configs[tokenId].complianceModules[]
    Asset-->>ERC: [0xModuleA, 0xModuleB]
    ERC->>Router: canTransfer(tokenId, from, to, amount)
    Router->>Module: moduleA.canTransfer() → (true, 0x0)
    Router->>Module: moduleB.canTransfer() → (true, 0x0)
    Router-->>ERC: true ✓ (todos os módulos aprovaram)

    Note over ERC: Etapa 5 — Execução
    ERC->>Balance: from.free -= amount
    ERC->>Balance: to.free += amount
    ERC->>Supply: atualizar rastreamento de holders
    ERC-->>User: emitir TransferSingle

    Note over ERC: Etapa 6 — Pós-Hook
    ERC->>Router: transferred(tokenId, from, to, amount)
    Router->>Module: moduleA.transferred(tokenId, from, to, amount)
    Router->>Module: moduleB.transferred(tokenId, from, to, amount)
